                "invention-title": [
                    "Integrated reforming hydrogen production system and reforming hydrogen production method",
                    "集成式重整制氢系统及重整制氢方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of reforming hydrogen production, in particular to an integrated reforming hydrogen production system which comprises a steam generator, a purification device, a gas mixing valve, a first induced draft fan, a reforming system, a heat exchanger, a water gas shift system and a pressure swing adsorption device. The gas outlet of the steam generator is also communicated with the gas inlet of the water-gas shift system; a heat recovery outlet of the heat exchanger is respectively communicated to the steam generator and the reforming system; the reforming system comprises a plurality of reforming reactors which are connected in parallel; the water gas conversion system comprises a plurality of water gas conversion reactors which are connected in parallel; the reforming reactor and the water gas shift reactor are cylindrical reactors; and the reforming reactors and the water-gas shift reactors are coaxially arranged in a one-to-one correspondence manner. In addition, the invention also relates to a reforming hydrogen production method. By highly integrating various processes, the hydrogen production efficiency can be greatly improved, the reforming hydrogen production operation process is greatly simplified, and the energy utilization efficiency of the hydrogen production system can be remarkably improved through the design of energy recovery."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及重整制氢技术领域，具体涉及一种集成式重整制氢系统，其包括蒸汽发生器、净化装置、混气阀、第一引风机、重整系统、换热器、水煤气变换系统和变压吸附装置；蒸汽发生器的出气口还连通水煤气变换系统的进气口；换热器的热量回收出口分别连通至蒸汽发生器和重整系统；重整系统包括多个并联的重整反应器，水煤气变换系统包括多个并联的水煤气变换反应器；重整反应器和水煤气变换反应器均为筒形反应器；重整反应器与水煤气变换反应器一一对应同轴布置。另外，本发明还涉及一种重整制氢方法。本发明将各种工艺高度集成可极大地提高制氢效率，重整制氢操作流程得到极大简化，能量回收的设计能显著地提高制氢系统的能量利用效率。"
                }
            ]
